<A>__{the sound of clocks constant ticking. mr. gateau at work...}
<C>__{daisy's }
<D>__{one day a letter came...}
<A>__{blanche comes into the workshop... a letter in her hand... she reads to her blind husband...}
<C>__{blanche devereux}
<D>__{"i am sorry to inform you that your son was killed fighting for his country, at the battle of the marne. in the death of sgt. martin gateau i lose one of my most trusted men.}
<C>__{blanche devereux }
<D>__{when i informed members of our company he had fallen, on every face could be seen the mark of sorrow... ...we were in hope the lord would spare him to return home together... alas this was not to be. i send along his pants, shirt, cavalry pin, kerchief, and haircomb."}
<C>__{daisy }
<D>__{mr. gateau, done for the night, went up to his bed.}
